<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"><p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;line-height: 107%;font-size: 11pt;font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;">Happy Monday folks.</p>
<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;line-height: 107%;font-size: 11pt;font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;">&nbsp;We are looking forward to seeing you at some of the events in the Hub this week, starting with the <a rel="noopener" href="https://carleton.ca/innovationhub/cu-events/networking-for-results-with-michael-j-hughes/">networking workshop at 5:00pm today</a>.&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;line-height: 107%;font-size: 11pt;font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;">Some of the Hatch and Changemaker participants who have been coming into the Hub are progressing well through the videos in Brightspace but have been asking for more opportunities to come in and meet with us and our mentors to chat about their strengths and their interests as they make decisions about their ventures, and about their future as an entrepreneur. &nbsp;To help you with that, we have pulled together a <span style="color: red;">resource(PDF attached</span>) for you to explore and then come in with.&nbsp; We have an open house and <a rel="noopener" href="https://carleton.ca/innovationhub/cu-events/innovation-hub-open-house-founder-check-in/">student/participant/founder check in</a> on Wednesday at 5:30 after the session with <a rel="noopener" href="https://carleton.ca/innovationhub/cu-events/interview-with-entrepreneur-sarah-james-jamieson/">Sarah James-Jamieson</a> at 4:00.</p>
<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;line-height: 107%;font-size: 11pt;font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;">We also have a <span style="color: red;">draft PPT document </span>to help you as you prepare your pitches for November 30. No need for your pitch slides to look like this but the information included is very important.&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;line-height: 107%;font-size: 11pt;font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;">Did you know that there is a $500 bursary available to one of the Hatch student founders pitching on that day who has overcome adversity during the term? Make sure that our mentors and our director know you and your story well before that day.</p>
<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt;line-height: 107%;font-size: 11pt;font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;">Please come in when you have time so that we can chat.</p>
<p style="margin: 0cm;font-size: 11pt;font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;"><b><a rel="noopener" href="https://carleton.ca/innovationhub/events/">Upcoming Events</a></b></p>
<ul style="margin-bottom: 0cm;margin-top: 0px;">
<li style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0px;font-size: 11pt;font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;"><b>Innovation Hub Events</b>
<ul style="list-style-type: circle;margin-bottom: 0cm;margin-top: 0px;">
<li style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0px;font-size: 11pt;font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;">4 - <a rel="noopener" href="https://carleton.ca/innovationhub/cu-events/networking-for-results-with-michael-j-hughes/">Networking for Results with Michael J. Hughes</a> @5:00pm</li>
<li style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0px;font-size: 11pt;font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;">6 - <a rel="noopener" href="https://carleton.ca/innovationhub/cu-events/interview-with-entrepreneur-sarah-james-jamieson/">Interview with Entrepreneur Sarah James-Jamieson</a> @4:00pm</li>
<li style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0px;font-size: 11pt;font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;">6 - <a rel="noopener" href="https://carleton.ca/innovationhub/cu-events/innovation-hub-open-house-founder-check-in/">November Open House &amp; Founder Check in</a> @ 5:30pm</li>
<li style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0px;font-size: 11pt;font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;">7 - <a rel="noopener" href="https://carleton.ca/innovationhub/cu-events/tim-lecture-series-guest-speaker-stephen-rayment/">TIM Lecture Series – Guest Speaker Stephen Rayment</a> @ 4pm in NI3040</li>
<li style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0px;font-size: 11pt;font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;">15-17 - <a rel="noopener" href="https://carleton.ca/innovationhub/cu-events/7460/">Crunch Startup Weekend</a> @ Algonquin College</li>
<li style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0px;font-size: 11pt;font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;">18 - <a rel="noopener" href="https://carleton.ca/innovationhub/cu-events/pitch-perfect-crafting-a-persuasive-message-that-converts-with-carl-richards/">Pitch Perfect: Crafting a Persuasive Message that Converts with Carl Richards</a> @ noon</li>
<li style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0px;font-size: 11pt;font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;">18 - <a rel="noopener" href="https://carleton.ca/innovationhub/cu-events/practice-makes-perfect-pitch-feedback-session-with-carl-richards/">Practice Makes Perfect: Pitch feedback session with Carl Richards</a> @ 4:30pm</li>
<li style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0px;font-size: 11pt;font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;">19 - <a rel="noopener" href="https://carleton.ca/innovationhub/cu-events/the-plantaform-story-interview-with-alberto-aguilar/">The Plantaform Story: Interview with Alberto Aguilar</a> @ 5:00pm</li>
<li style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0px;font-size: 11pt;font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;">22 <a rel="noopener" href="https://carleton.ca/innovationhub/cu-events/capital-kickstart-your-guide-to-fundraising-success-with-julie-mcclure/">- Capital Kickstart: Your Guide to Fundraising Success with Julie McClure</a> @ 3:00pm</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<p style="margin: 0cm;font-size: 11pt;font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</p>
<ul style="margin-bottom: 0cm;margin-top: 0px;">
<li style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0px;font-size: 11pt;font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;"><b>Community Events</b>
<ul style="list-style-type: circle;margin-bottom: 0cm;margin-top: 0px;">
<li style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0px;font-size: 11pt;font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;">5 - <a rel="noopener" href="https://carleton.ca/innovationhub/cu-events/techtuesday-building-a-global-tech-hub/">TechTuesday: Building a Global Tech Hub</a> @ 5pm</li>
<li style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0px;font-size: 11pt;font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;">6 - <a rel="noopener" href="https://carleton.ca/innovationhub/cu-events/turn-fear-into-fuel-a-masterclass-in-taking-smart-risks-for-startup-found/?preview_id=7881&amp;preview_nonce=77421d571c&amp;preview=true">Turn Fear into Fuel: A Masterclass in Taking Smart Risks for Startup Founders</a></li>
<li style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0px;font-size: 11pt;font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;">8 - <a rel="noopener" href="https://carleton.ca/innovationhub/cu-events/tiecon-canada-2024-disruptive-entrepreneurship-ai-emerging-technology/">TiECon Canada 2024 – Disruptive Entrepreneurship – AI &amp; Emerging Technology</a></li>
<li style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0px;font-size: 11pt;font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;">12 -&nbsp;&nbsp; <a rel="noopener" href="https://carleton.ca/innovationhub/cu-events/adventure-with-cvca-at-carleton-university/">adVENTURE with CVCA at Carleton University</a></li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<p style="margin: 0cm;font-size: 11pt;font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin: 0cm;font-size: 11pt;font-family: Aptos, sans-serif;">Have a wonderful week.</p>
